msg":"錶帶爛左有冇巴打知邊度有得買？用緊fenix 2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b156bfd36d583bf69f7e5c4ddb74a6087776647","tid":23562,"uid":17546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T05:40:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>錶帶爛左有冇巴打知邊度有得買？用緊fenix 2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nfenix 2錶帶個扣真係世界級垃圾 次次都係爛個扣 換第2條帶又係爛個扣<br />\n依家連條帶都爛埋 放棄等FENIX 5"},{"pid":"4f8aa652dd0c0fa4da2e1d56bad661869e10d843","tid":23562,"uid":32006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T05:29:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>錶帶爛左有冇巴打知邊度有得買？用緊fenix 2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nfenix 2錶帶個扣真係世界級垃圾 次次都係爛個扣 換第2條帶又係爛個扣<br />\n依家連條帶都爛埋 放棄等FENIX 5</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我買fenix 2係因為我本身都好鍾意gshock外形d野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係買完之後，fenix 2問題多多: <br />\n最嚴重: 跑完步禁收工制會hand機，果日跑完d data睇唔返<br />\n普通嚴重: 跑跑下明明有50%電，會無啦啦hand機，呢個情況多數係train佢d fitness plan會，如果淨用run好少出事<br />\n濕碎野: Bluetooth connect成日connect唔到an狗手機，錶帶用左一年多d就爛，平時都叫錫住帶，睇唔到中文比whatsapp notification我做乜9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，GPS locate得慢(唔知係咪隻隻都係)<br />\n<br />\n上面d問題係咪fenix 3就解決左？<br />\nbetween<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />想請問下有冇巴打有用開sunnoto，係咪少d派膠？"},{"pid":"e54427578dab40ebdc10918909f5a9fde8f4c78b","tid":23562,"uid":4611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T16:49:15.000Z","msg":"新加盟fenix 3用家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b32007402ebbea828c68af1cee7dcd0f95a32008","tid":23562,"uid":13807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T13:48:25.000Z","msg":"如果想行山 跑步 跳繩用 235夠唔夠做？<br />\n諗緊買唔買235 跪求意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img 